/figcaption>\n    </figure>\n\n  <p>Netflix is following up the Mike Tyson vs. Jake Paul fight with NFL games and WWE\u2019s Monday Night Raw.</p>\n  <p>\n    <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/24300871/netflix-live-events-nfl-celebrity-boxing\">Continue reading&hellip;</a>\n  </p>\n\n", "id": 1551011, "language": null, "link": "https://www.theverge.com/24300871/netflix-live-events-nfl-celebrity-boxing", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 359, "source_url": "https://www.theverge.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "NFL, celebrity boxing, and hot dogs: Netflix\u2019s push into live TV", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-11-20T09:00:00+00:00", "description": "  \n\n    <figure>\n      <img alt=\"A screenshot from the video game S.T.A.L.K.E.R. 2: Heart of Chornobyl.\" src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/R1NJdszWTzrvjMyYR-TQXLL74CI=/0x0:3240x2160/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73735557/S2HoC_GSCGameWorld_Richter.0.jpg\" />\n        <figcaption>Image: GSC Game World</figcaption>\n    </figure>\n\n\n  \t\t <p>GSC Game World\u2019s long-awaited survival epic delivers the ultimate stalker fantasy \u2014 if you can look beyond the plethora of glitches.</p>\n  <p>\n    <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/20/24300652/stalker-2-heart-of-chornobyl-review\">Continue reading&hellip;</a>\n  </p>\n\n", "id": 1551012, "language": null, "link": "https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/20/24300652/stalker-2-heart-of-chornobyl-review", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 359, "source_url": "https://www.theverge.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "S.T.A.L.K.E.R. 2: Heart of Chornobyl is a glorious and beautiful pain in the ass", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-11-20T08:23:28+00:00", "description": "  \n\n    <figure>\n      <img alt=\"Comcast\u2019s Xfinity Mobile Service Introduces New 5G Unlimited Data Options\" src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/qGiEnWcbDST-mEWXomkWUXmmbYw=/0x0:6240x4160/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73735488/1232480654.0.jpg\" />\n        <figcaption>Photo by Jeff Fusco/Getty Images for Comcast</figcaption>\n    </figure>\n\n  <p id=\"cWZdHN\">Comcast is splitting from its NBCUniversal television arm as the market of cable TV customers shrinks in the age of cord-cutting and TikTok.</p>\n<p id=\"PFfHik\">The US media giant <a href=\"https://www.cmcsa.com/news-releases/news-release-details/comcast-announces-intention-create-leading-independent-media\">announced plans on Wednesday to spin off </a>the bulk of its cable network channels \u2014 including CNBC, MSNBC, Universal Kids, USA Network, E!, Oxygen, Golf Channel, and Syfy \u2014 into a separate company. Comcast will retain its reality TV darling Bravo and the Peacock streaming service within its NBC TV business. ", "id": 1551013, "language": null, "link": "https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/20/24301310/comcast-spinning-off-nbcuniversal-cable-tv-business", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 359, "source_url": "https://www.theverge.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Comcast is spinning off its cable TV business", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-11-20T08:08:43+00:00", "description": "  \n\n    <figure>\n      <img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/wVlrgnpVrfPlH-fz__-AB_azHFo=/150x0:1770x1080/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73735469/Gb0q8GcXcAQ7_bb.0.jpg\" />\n        <figcaption><em>Reviews for the game on Steam are currently labeled as \u201cOverwhelmingly Negative.\u201d</em> | Image: <em>Microsoft Flight Simulator 2024</em></figcaption>\n    </figure>\n\n  <p id=\"kCXrMK\"><em>Microsoft Flight Simulator 2024</em> was released on PC and Xbox yesterday but early players have struggled to load or even finish installing the game. Users have reported a range of issues \u2014 including post-installation loads stalling before completion, long login queues, and the game itself crashing \u2014 with the $70 flying sim <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/app/2537590/reviews/?browsefilter=toprated&amp;snr=1_5_100010_\">currently tagged as \u201cOverwhelmingly Negative\u201d</a> in customer reviews on Steam.</p>\n<p id=\"KLuC3H\">Some players are seeing their downloads freeze at 97 perc", "id": 1550607, "language": null, "link": "https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/20/24301358/microsoft-flight-simulator-2024-launch-day-issues", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 359, "source_url": "https://www.theverge.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Microsoft Flight Simulator 2024 wasn\u2019t prepared for takeoff", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-11-20T08:00:00+00:00", "description": "  \n\n    <figure>\n      <img alt=\"Illustration of Google\u2019s wordmark, written in red and pink on a dark blue background.\" src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/UakaVcwwd3Y-FYvCZgnkUTXP6iY=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73735397/STK093_Google_06.0.jpg\" />\n        <figcaption>Illustration: The Verge</figcaption>\n    </figure>\n\n  <p id=\"EhMYkk\">Google employees met with the Department of Just